defaultwelcomes
default this opportunity to provide input to the Select Committee’s Inquiry into the Strategic Road Network
default 
default(SRN)
default.
default&#xa0;
defaultThe SELTB is working closely with the South East Local Enterprise Partnership (SELEP), local authorities and businesses in the preparation of SELEP
default’s Strategic Economic Plan. The LEP-wide growth priorities emerging from this work 
defaultclearly require
default a 
defaulthigh quality SRN to provide real and direct economic benefits. 
